The app1_new.py is using alternate retrieval method. The retrieval is keyword based retrirval of relavant documents.

For app1_new.py Water.pdf and Water1.pdf are the document used. after1.html and answer1.html will be the template files.

To execute the code : python app1_new.py

Then copy the localhost address from your cmd/terminal and open it in your browser to see the system in action.


Additional Package used:

autocorrect https://pypi.org/project/autocorrect/


EvaluateQA_Water is evaluation for app1_new.py (New retriever keyword based)

EvaluateQA is evaluation for app1 (original retriever BM25L)
